high_descs: Turn right and go across the room to counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Move over to the right to the fridge.
Put the fork in the cup in the fridge.
Take the bowl with the fork in it out of the fridge.
Turn left and go across the room to the sink.
Put the cup and fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup with a fork in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and then turn to your left to face the coffee maker
Pick up a spoon off of the counter
Move to your right and turn to face the fridge
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the cup that is in the fridge
Pick up the cup from the fridge and close the fridge door
Turn left twice and then turn to your right to face the sink
Put the cup with spoon in it in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a cup and put them both in the sink

high_descs: Go to the right and then turn left towards the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick the fork up from the counter.
Move to the right and face the fridge.
Put the fork in the bowl in the fridge.
Pick the bowl up from the shelf in the fridge and close the door.
Go left and cross the room to stand in front of the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a fork in it in the sink.
